    public abstract class RandomizableParallelMultipleClassifiersCombiner
extends ParallelMultipleClassifiersCombiner
implements Randomizable
    Abstract utility class for handling settings common to meta classifiers that build an ensemble in parallel using multiple classifiers based on a given random number seed.

      • setOptions

        public void setOptions(java.lang.String[] options)
                throws java.lang.Exception
        Parses a given list of options. Valid options are:

        -B classifierstring
        Classifierstring should contain the full class name of a scheme included for selection followed by options to the classifier (required, option should be used once for each classifier).

        -S num
        Set the random number seed (default 1).

        Specified by:
